temos el agua en el hueco</li>\n                <li>Disolvemos la levadura en el agua con la mano</li>\n                <li>Mezclamos todo</li>\n                <li>Si queremos ponerle sal se pone ahora ya que si no interfiere con la levadura</li>\n                <li>Amasamos haciendo plieges durante 5-10 minutos</li>\n                <li>Dejamos fermentar 8 horas a temperatura ambiente o 16 horas en la nevera</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </body>\n</html>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/image {\"block_id\":\"dd91113b\",\"url\":\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/masas-de-pizza-NY-e1405888294177.jpg\",\"urlTablet\":\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/masas-de-pizza-NY-e1405888294177.jpg\",\"urlMobile\":\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/masas-de-pizza-NY-e1405888294177.jpg\",\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":82,\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"title\":\"masas-de-pizza-NY-e1405888294177\",\"width\":900,\"height\":240,\"naturalWidth\":1024,\"naturalHeight\":488,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"sizeSlugTablet\":\"full\",\"sizeSlugMobile\":\"full\",\"customHeightSetDesktop\":true,\"imageBorderTopWidth\":4,\"imageBorderLeftWidth\":4,\"imageBorderRightWidth\":4,\"imageBorderBottomWidth\":4,\"imageBorderTopLeftRadius\":80,\"imageBorderTopRightRadius\":80,\"imageBorderBottomLeftRadius\":80,\"imageBorderBottomRightRadius\":80,\"imageBorderStyle\":\"solid\",\"imageBorderColor\":\"var(\\u002d\\u002dglobal-palette2)\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-image aligncenter uagb-block-dd91113b wp-block-uagb-image--layout-default wp-block-uagb-image--effect-static wp-block-uagb-image--align-center\"><figure class=\"wp-block-uagb-image__figure\"><img srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/masas-de-pizza-NY-e1405888294177.jpg ,http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/masas-de-pizza-NY-e1405888294177.jpg 780w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/masas-de-pizza-NY-e1405888